{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Console.time()","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/time","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Console_API\">Console API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console\"><code>Console</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methoden</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/assert\"><code>assert()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/clear\"><code>clear()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/count\"><code>count()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/countReset\"><code>countReset()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/debug\"><code>debug()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/dir\"><code>dir()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/dirxml\"><code>dirxml()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/error\"><code>error()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/group\"><code>group()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/groupCollapsed\"><code>groupCollapsed()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/groupEnd\"><code>groupEnd()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/info\"><code>info()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/log\"><code>log()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/profile\"><code>profile()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/profileEnd\"><code>profileEnd()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/table\"><code>table()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/time\"><code>time()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/timeEnd\"><code>timeEnd()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/timeLog\"><code>timeLog()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/timeStamp\"><code>timeStamp()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/trace\"><code>trace()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/warn\"><code>warn()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ähnliche Seiten zu Console API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Window/console\"><code>Window.console</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/console\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.console</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Startet&nbsp;einen&nbsp;Timer, den man benutzen kann, um zu überprüfen wie&nbsp;lange&nbsp;eine&nbsp;bestimmte&nbsp;Operation. Man kann&nbsp;jedem Timer einen&nbsp;einzigartigen Namen geben&nbsp;und kann&nbsp;bis zu 10000 Timer gleichzeitig auf einer Seite laufen lassen. Wenn man <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/timeEnd\"><code>console.timeEnd()</code></a> mit dem selben Namen aufruft, gibt der Browser die Zeit in Millisekunden zurück, die seit dem Starten des Timers verstrichen ist.</p>\n\n<p>Siehe auch&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console#timers\">Timer</a>&nbsp;in der <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console\"><code>console</code></a> Dokumentation für weitere Details und Beispiele.</p>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\">\n  <p><strong>Hinweis:</strong> Dieses Feature ist in <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Workers</a> verfügbar</p>\n</div><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">console.time(<em>Bezeichnung</em>);\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameter","title":"Parameter","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"bezeichnung\"><code>Bezeichnung</code></dt>\n <dd>Der Name des neuen Timers. Dieser wird den Timer identifizieren; Der selbe Name sollte beim aufrufen von <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/timeEnd\"><code>console.timeEnd()</code></a> genutzt werden, um den Timer zu stoppen und das Ergebnis in die Konsole zu drucken.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://console.spec.whatwg.org/#time\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Console API<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'console.time()' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"data":null,"query":"api.Console.time","browsers":null}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/timeEnd\"><code>Console.timeEnd()</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.opera.com/dragonfly/documentation/console/\" rel=\" noopener\">Opera Dragonfly documentation: Console</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Parameter","id":"parameter"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Startet einen Timer, den man benutzen kann, um zu überprüfen wie lange eine bestimmte Operation. Man kann jedem Timer einen einzigartigen Namen geben und kann bis zu 10000 Timer gleichzeitig auf einer Seite laufen lassen. Wenn man console.timeEnd() mit dem selben Namen aufruft, gibt der Browser die Zeit in Millisekunden zurück, die seit dem Starten des Timers verstrichen ist.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"console.time()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Console.time()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"console.time","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"console.time()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"console.time()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Console.time()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Console.time()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"console.time","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/console/time","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/console/time/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Console","title":"Console"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/time","title":"Console.time()"}],"pageTitle":"Console.time() - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}